title: 2021 North 2 Region wrestling: Final results (Reg. 3 & 4)
body: 2021 NJSIAA North 2 Region Wrestling ChampionshipsThe best high school boys wrestlers in New Jersey open pursuit of state titles on Saturday with the opening round of the NJSIAA/Rothman Orthopaedics wrestling tournament.The North Jersey, Section 2 Region tournament is set for Union High School.Complete results are on the way from , so stay tuned.The final round:4-, Delbarton d. 2-, South Plainfield, 4-1.2-, Seton Hall Prep d. 1-, West Morris, 4-1.1-, Delbarton md. 3-, Roselle Park, 11-1.2-, Delbarton d. 4-, North Hunterdon, 6-3.1-, Delbarton d. 3-, Brearley, 6-4.1-, Hanover Park p. 3-, Elizabeth, 3:05.1-, Delbarton d. 2-, South Plainfield, 3-1 (SV).Note to readers: if you purchase something through one of our affiliate links we may earn a commission.
